channel.title: HEEEEELPPP read this!
channel.description:
Hello,
I was a week with my dad, and i made a server. I took my laptop to him, and i got a IP. Everything work perfect. But i was going to my mother with the same laptop. And they give me another IP, that's no-problem, cuz i got a site. But when i run my server, and i type the IP in, Then it says "error connecting to server". But why? I try on the computer of my brother, and i got the same problem.. I ask a friend, to play on my server; And he got an "Error connecting to server.".
Please, HELP!!! :confused:
The server got over 35 ppl, and i can't play on it, nobody can play on it! Help me plz, i need it.. ;D
THANK YOU!
